    <string>Allow PhotoLynk to use the camera to scan QR codes for server pairing.</string>
    <key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
    <string>PhotoLynk uses Face ID to unlock your account for quick auto-login without entering your password.</string>
    <key>NSLocalNetworkUsageDescription</key>
    <string>PhotoLynk needs access to your local network to discover and connect to your PhotoLynk server for photo backup.</string>
    <key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Allow $(PRODUCT_NAME) to access your microphone</string>
    <key>NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription</key>
    <string>PhotoLynk saves photos and videos you restore or export from your backup back into your library.</string>
    <key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
    <string>PhotoLynk needs read access to choose photos and videos to back up from your device to your PhotoLynk account.</string>
